entries.title_d: A vessel's signature has been spotted leaving the surface of Dathomir. Capture and inspect this vessel. The Inquisition is very interested to find out what is on board.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Inspect the Crystal Smuggler
entries.split_quest_alert: Hold current position for further instructions.
entries.quest_location_d: The ship has just left Dathomir's surface. Intercept it before it is able to leave the system. A navigation waypoint to its most recent location will be supplied to you.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Disable and inspect the smuggler's cargo.
entries.quest_dock_d: Once you have discovered what the smuggler was carrying, dock with his ship and transfer the cargo to your ship.
